CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 18, reads: "...7. Lamar Hunsicker and Joe Karee let homemakers sample their various cheese products in the Joseph Karee-Dairyland Cheese Company booth..."
TitMainTitle: Women standing in front of Lamar Hunsicker and Joe Karee at counter of Joseph Karee-Dairyland Cheese Company booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
